      "id": "case-study_aspire-x-careerspan-proposal_5dd789b1",
      "key_findings": [
        "Historical Aspire cohort of 627 invited alumni produced 87 stories, 103 resumes and 84 job fit checks with 155 fully activated users (about 24% activation).",
        "AI content costs were roughly 453 dollars versus about 12,300 dollars of equivalent human coaching value, yielding roughly 27x ROI.",
        "The proposal scales to a 1,000-learner, 6-month program assuming around 16% activation and roughly double the usage depth per active alumnus versus the prior Aspire cohort.",
        "Projected AI content cost for the scaled program is about 950 dollars, delivering an estimated 246 hours (around 24.6k dollars) of coaching-equivalent support."
      ],
