      "key_findings": [
        "92% of students said Careerspan strengthened the standout experiences they wanted to highlight.",
        "80% reported discovering additional experiences or stories they would not have emphasized before.",
        "Confidence in talking about experiences in interviews/networking increased by 12.3% on a 1\u20135 scale.",
        "Engagement was strong: 247 story starts with 218 completions, low abandonment and multiple peaks beyond deadline-driven usage.",
        "Qualitative themes included specificity, recognition of transferable skills, better professional communication and improved tailoring to target roles."
      ],
